channel.title: Need A Webclient O.O
channel.description:
Hey people! I'm Rave Oni the owner of oniscape =]
Ive been trying for a while to make my client a web client. I get lots of problems though such as: Interfaces, Error Connecting to Server, File Bin, Cache, etc.
So i'm asking you to make one for me!!! =D, this will be difficult though because this client is [I think] bluurr\delta scape. [Don't call me stupid IDC, much better at designing servers than clients XD] The client URL is: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=E1L27YVO. You cannot find this on the oniscape website yet because it is officially for the web client.
If you don't want to I understand, BUT! Don't reply saying some crap like: OMFG I MADE A WEBCLIENT FOR MY FRIEND! HAHAH IM SMARTER THAN YOU. That is just plain crap. If you don't want to make it, refer me to a tutorial that can make it, or tell me yourself. And don't give me shetty help like: #1 You add coding, #2 You compile, #3 You upload. That is even more crap than the first one!
Kk well I guess you understand what i'm saying. Cyah later, ~Rave Oni, Owner of OniScape
